ZH: 他们交替着工作。
EN: They take turns working.

ZH: 孩子们在游戏中交替扮演不同的角色。
EN: The children take turns playing different roles in the game.

ZH: 我们在轮流交替做饭。
EN: We take turns cooking.

ZH: 到了夏天，白天和黑夜交替得很快。
EN: In summer, day and night alternate quickly.

ZH: 这个舞蹈需要两个人交替跳。
EN: The dance requires two people to take turns dancing.

ZH: 他们用不同的颜色的纸条来交替装饰墙壁。
EN: They use different colored paper strips to alternate decorating the walls.

ZH: 他们交替在轮椅上推行。
EN: They take turns pushing the wheelchair.

ZH: 这个任务需要两个人交替完成。
EN: This task requires two people to alternate completing it.

ZH: 他们在比赛中不断交替领先。
EN: They alternately take the lead in the competition.

ZH: 剧情交替展现了不同角度的故事。
EN: The plot alternately presents different perspectives of the story.

ZH: 冬天和春天在交替之中。
EN: Winter and spring are alternating.

ZH: 队员们在场上交替换防守和进攻。
EN: The players alternate defense and offense on the field.

ZH: 天气交替变化，时晴时雨。
EN: The weather alternates between sunshine and rain.

ZH: 这两种颜色会交替出现在图案里。
EN: These two colors will alternate in the pattern.

ZH: 他们交替着担任会议主席。
EN: They take turns serving as the chairman of the meeting.

ZH: 这两个演员在戏剧中交替扮演主角。
EN: These two actors alternate playing the lead role in the play.

ZH: 在生活中，好运和坏运总是交替出现。
EN: In life, good luck and bad luck always alternate.

ZH: 他们交替着轮流练习弹琴。
EN: They take turns practicing playing the piano.

ZH: 两国交替举办奥运会。
EN: The two countries alternate hosting the Olympics.

ZH: 这两种食材要交替添加到菜肴中。
EN: These two ingredients need to be alternately added to the dish.
